<p id="fs-idp96882128"><a class="autogenerated-content" href="#CNX_Chem_14_02_phscale">Figure 14.2</a> shows the relationships between [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>], [OH<sup>−</sup>], pH, and pOH for solutions classified as acidic, basic, and neutral.</p>

